**Quality Gates**
- For every new module: header with purpose, inputs/outputs, example curl/use.
- Enforce scripts:
  - dev: nodemon --exec ts-node src/server.ts
  - ingest: ts-node src/jobs/ingest.ts
  - migrate: prisma migrate dev
  - typecheck: tsc --noEmit
- Require a short test plan (curl examples) before marking a step “done”.